data.description:
Back on the market at no fault to seller. Unfortunately, this seller is having to relocate due to the military! Come and check out this beautiful home they hate to leave!
 Welcome home to this beautifully maintained 3 bedroom/2 bath home built by Jonathan Overholt. As you enter you will walk into a beautiful open floor plan that has wood flooring throughout the dining and living area. If you enjoy natural light, this is the house for you! NO CARPET! Each bedroom features LVP flooring. Enjoy the tranquility of the outdoors on the screened-in back porch. The perfectly sized master bedroom has a master bath that has an oversized tub and his & her sink with a walk-in closet.
In this quaint home you will find fresh paint, new light fixtures, new ceiling fans, dishwasher and a less than 4-year-old HVAC system!
This community features a community pool for everyone to enjoy during these hot days! Minutes to FLETC, beaches at St Simons Island & Jekyll Island. Short drive to Savannah or Jacksonville, FL.
